{"tid":113011,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"製作有聲講故台，希望各位巴絲打俾D意見","createTime":"2017-02-08T15:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T02:32:51.000Z","uid":26449,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2356bd67e597beacae26944199112774fc681cdb","tid":113011,"uid":26449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"小弟最近做緊一個Siri講故仔既YouTube頻道，希望唔鍾意閱讀既朋友都知道網上小說既有趣之處。<br />\n<br />\n暫時做緊天黑莫回頭，背後不是人得故事（已得到沙士被壓巴打同意轉載）希望各位可以俾D意見改善。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一章：飄浮的屍體<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wXHXqh09X68\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwXHXqh09X68&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=239398de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wXHXqh09X68</a><br />\n加左雨聲音效，好似唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二章：抬不起的棺材<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J1PF5NlATGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ1PF5NlATGQ&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0be6fbf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J1PF5NlATGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n第三章：紅線<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iyKLQs82db8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiyKLQs82db8&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=88ec5d13\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iyKLQs82db8</a><br />\n<br />\n其他會陸續更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffcf222af61ccee06ebc8be0abcace25ae7372c","tid":113011,"uid":27831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"Lm 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856d70c449f3a898a9c7ceeaa4bba552e93f75cb","tid":113011,"uid":53118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"唔siri得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},